module uppercut
def desc You jump and it works as a trigger bot (I think that is really good i found some video on YT and someone said to make this for him if possible so i did xD, also it might be perfect crit timing)

on tick {
    if input_active jump {
        if holding #sword {
            if attack_progress >=0.9 {
                if target_entity :player {
                    input left
                }
            }
        }
    }
}